<!-- Account Deletion Section -->
<section id="account-deletion" style="margin-top: 50px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-family: sans-serif;">
    <h2 style="color: #d32f2f;">Request Account Deletion</h2>
    <p>According to Google Play's Data Safety requirements, you may request the permanent deletion of your JDRB Water Billing account and all associated data.</p>
    
    <div style="background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #eee;">
        <p><strong>What will be deleted:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your user profile and authentication credentials.</li>
            <li>All your registered Clients, Bills, and Payment records.</li>
            <li>All saved app configurations and settings.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><em>Note: This action is irreversible. Once deleted, your data cannot be recovered.</em></p>

        <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;">

        <h3>Submit Deletion Request</h3>
        <p>To request deletion, please email us at <strong>rexel50@gmail.com</strong> from your registered email address, or fill out the shortcut below:</p>
        
        <form action="mailto:rexel50@gmail.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <label>Your Registered Email Address:</label><br>
                <input type="email" name="Email" required style="width: 100%; padding: 8px; margin-top: 5px;">
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <label>Reason (Optional):</label><br>
                <textarea name="Reason" style="width: 100%; padding: 8px; margin-top: 5px;"></textarea>
            </div>
            <input type="hidden" name="Subject" value="Account Deletion Request - JDRB Water Billing">
            <button type="submit" style="background-color: #d32f2f; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;">
                Send Deletion Request
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>
